00:06:42.250 --> 00:06:45.080
Wah rinci sekali gambar ini.

00:06:45.080 --> 00:06:47.040
Saten-san, Saten-san!

00:06:47.040 --> 00:06:49.000
Sepertinya kita bisa mengalaminya loh!

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:51.500
Baiklah, baiklah, aku mengerti.

00:06:51.500 --> 00:06:54.670
